{"type":"message","id":"32e3251c","parentId":"5d3a8b7f","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:05:54.730Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me try with a simpler stock first to see if the API works at all. Let me try the EODHD tool with a US stock first to verify the API works, and then try the Chinese stock in a different format.\n\nActually, wait - the error says \"缺少必需的查询参数: 'codes'\" which means \"Missing required query parameter: 'codes'\". This seems to be a server-side issue with the ths_ifind tool. The tool may have a bug or the parameters are being sent incorrectly.\n\nLet me try using the EODHD API to get Chinese stocks with their format (which might use different ticker symbols).","thinkingSignature":"565e966fb82a3c374e8c736eeaebbd6e4419200045efd4dcd25fbd65a87bfa66"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gilmzcoleb87_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && QVERIS_API_KEY=$QVERIS_API_KEY node -e \"\nconst API_KEY = process.env.QVERIS_API_KEY;\nconst API_BASE = 'https://qveris.ai/api/v1';\n\nasync function execute() {\n  // Try EODHD with a US stock first to test\n  const res = await fetch(\\`\\${API_BASE}/tools/execute\\`, {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': \\`Bearer \\${API_KEY}\\`\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ \n      tool_id: 'eodhd.live_prices.retrieve.v1.178541d4', \n      params: { ticker: 'AAPL.US' }\n    })\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  console.log(JSON.stringify(data, null, 2));\n}\n\nexecute();\n\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":18238,"output":353,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32575,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772600738724}}
