{"type":"message","id":"0ab8a31d","parentId":"84290a5f","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:09:35.466Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dzpme27c0x9b_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"stock price API China\",\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.real_time_quotation.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺实时行情 (THS Real-time Quotation)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query real-time quotation data for securities in the 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database, providing real-time market data for financial products including stocks, funds, bonds, and futures, such as real-time prices, trading volumes, price changes, bid/ask quotes, etc. Supports querying various real-time indicators including latest price, price change, trading volume, turnover ratio, market value, and five-level bid/ask quotes.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"indicators\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Indicator list, multiple indicators separated by commas. Options: 'common' (common indicators), 'all' (all indicators), or custom indicator list. Default is 'all'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"codes\": \"300033.SZ,600030.SH\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1667.64,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.887\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.hk_connect_stats.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 沪深港通交易统计 (HK Stock Connect Trading Stats)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query Shanghai-Shenzhen-Hong Kong Stock Connect trading statistics from 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database. Covers northbound (沪股通, 深股通) and southbound (港股通沪市, 港股通深市) channels. Returns trading volume, buy/sell amounts, net buy amount, transaction counts, and top-10 active stocks concentration ratios. Supports daily, weekly, monthly, and yearly aggregation. Useful for tracking cross-border capital flows between mainland China and Hong Kong markets.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sdate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Start date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"edate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"End date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"zq\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Aggregation period. Valid values: 'day', 'week', 'month', 'year'. Defaults to 'week'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"lx\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Channel type filter. 'ALL'=all channels, '1'=沪股通, '2'=港股通(沪市), '3'=深股通, '4'=港股通(深市). Defaults to 'ALL'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"bz\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Currency for amounts. Defaults to 'CNY'.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 715.71,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.532\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"nbsc_data.(current.price).v2.A0101\",\n      \"name\": \"National Quarterly Data Gdp (current Price)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query National Quarterly Data Gdp (current Price) statistical data from the National Bureau of Statistics of China. Data source: National quarterly data. Provides price indices including consumer prices and producer prices. Data available for periods 2024B to 2025C.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"m\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"API method name. Valid values: \\\"QueryData\\\" - queries statistical data from the database.\",\n            \"zh\": \"API方法名称。有效值：\\\"QueryData\\\" - 从数据库查询统计数据。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"QueryData\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"dbcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Database code specifying the data type and granularity. Valid values: \\\"hgjd\\\" - national quarterly data.\",\n            \"zh\": \"数据库代码，指定数据类型和粒度。有效值：\\\"hgjd\\\" - 全国季度数据。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"hgjd\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"rowcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Row dimension code specifying what appears in rows. Valid values: \\\"zb\\\" - indicators (statistical metrics), \\\"sj\\\" - time periods (years, quarters, months), \\\"reg\\\" - regions (provinces, cities).\",\n            \"zh\": \"行维度代码，指定行中显示的内容。有效值：\\\"zb\\\" - 指标（统计指标），\\\"sj\\\" - 时间（年、季度、月），\\\"reg\\\" - 地区（省、市）。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"zb\",\n            \"sj\",\n            \"reg\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"colcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Column dimension code specifying what appears in columns. Valid values: \\\"zb\\\" - indicators (statistical metrics), \\\"sj\\\" - time periods (years, quarters, months), \\\"reg\\\" - regions (provinces, cities).\",\n            \"zh\": \"列维度代码，指定列中显示的内容。有效值：\\\"zb\\\" - 指标（统计指标），\\\"sj\\\" - 时间（年、季度、月），\\\"reg\\\" - 地区（省、市）。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"zb\",\n            \"sj\",\n            \"reg\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"wds\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Fixed WHERE dimensions as a JSON array string. Used for additional filtering conditions. Typically use \\\"[]\\\" for empty (no additional filters).\",\n            \"zh\": \"固定WHERE维度，JSON数组字符串。用于附加筛选条件。通常使用\\\"[]\\\"表示空（无附加筛选）。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"dfwds\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Default WHERE dimensions as a JSON array string. Specifies the main filter criteria. For this indicator, use: [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"zb\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"A0101\\\"}] to query by indicator code, or add [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"sj\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"YYYY\\\"}] to filter by specific year.\",\n            \"zh\": \"默认WHERE维度，JSON数组字符串。指定主要筛选条件。对于此指标，使用：[{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"zb\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"A0101\\\"}] 按指标代码查询，或添加 [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"sj\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"YYYY\\\"}] 按特定年份筛选。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"k1\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Timestamp in milliseconds. Used to prevent response caching. Optional - can be omitted or set to current timestamp in milliseconds.\",\n            \"zh\": \"时间戳（毫秒）。用于防止响应缓存。可选 - 可以省略或设置为当前时间戳（毫秒）。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"h\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Optional parameter, typically set to \\\"1\\\". Can be omitted.\",\n            \"zh\": \"可选参数，通常设置为\\\"1\\\"。可以省略。\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"m\": \"QueryData\",\n          \"k1\": \"1766394071574\",\n          \"wds\": \"[]\",\n          \"dfwds\": \"[{\\\"wdcode\\\": \\\"zb\\\", \\\"valuecode\\\": \\\"A0101\\\"}]\",\n          \"dbcode\": \"hgjd\",\n          \"colcode\": \"sj\",\n          \"rowcode\": \"zb\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Data from the National Bureau of Statistics of China (NBSC). This provider offers comprehensive access to official Chinese economic and social statistics data including GDP, population, employment, prices, trade, and more. All data is sourced directly from the official National Bureau of Statistics of China website. The API provides annual, quarterly, and monthly data covering various economic indicators. Data includes national statistics, provincial statistics, major cities data, and Hong Kong, Macao, Taiwan data. No authentication is required to access the public statistics data. This provider includes 107 tools covering different statistical indicators from multiple data sources.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 850.39,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.419\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.company_basics.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 公司基础信息 (Company Basics)\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieve the latest (or a specific date) company basics indicators from THS iFinD. Includes company name, industry, comparable/peer companies, concept tags, codes, established date, registration info, main business, and major products.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, comma-separated (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"date\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Date, format: 'YYYYMMDD'. Use this field to query historical values. Defaults to latest.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 780.08,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.914\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.etf_constituents.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD ETF成分股票列表 (ETF Constituent Stock List)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query the constituent stock list of an ETF from 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database. Returns detailed information about each constituent stock including stock code, name, share quantity, cash substitution flag, subscription/redemption premium ratios and fixed substitution amounts. Useful for analyzing ETF composition and tracking ETF holdings.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"thscode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"ETF security code, e.g., '510300.SH', '159001.SZ'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"date\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Query date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'. Defaults to today.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 644.44,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.91\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub_io_api.stock.quote\",\n      \"name\": \"Quote\",\n      \"description\": \"Get real-time quote data for US stocks.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Stock symbol\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 853.46,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.951\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"nbsc_data.self-employed.v2.635e8422\",\n      \"name\": \"Self-employed\",\n      \"description\": \"Query Self-employed statistical data from the National Bureau of Statistics of China. Provides employment statistics including workforce numbers and wage data. Data available for years 2015 to 2024.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"m\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"API method name. Valid values: \\\"QueryData\\\" - queries statistical data from the database.\",\n            \"zh\": \"API方法名称。有效值：\\\"QueryData\\\" - 从数据库查询统计数据。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"QueryData\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"dbcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Database code specifying the data type and granularity. Valid values: \\\"hgnd\\\" - national annual data, \\\"hgjd\\\" - national quarterly data, \\\"hgyd\\\" - national monthly data, \\\"fsnd\\\" - provincial annual data, \\\"fsjd\\\" - provincial quarterly data, \\\"fsyd\\\" - provincial monthly data.\",\n            \"zh\": \"数据库代码，指定数据类型和粒度。有效值：\\\"hgnd\\\" - 全国年度数据，\\\"hgjd\\\" - 全国季度数据，\\\"hgyd\\\" - 全国月度数据，\\\"fsnd\\\" - 分省年度数据，\\\"fsjd\\\" - 分省季度数据，\\\"fsyd\\\" - 分省月度数据。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"hgnd\",\n            \"hgjd\",\n            \"hgyd\",\n            \"fsnd\",\n            \"fsjd\",\n            \"fsyd\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"rowcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Row dimension code specifying what appears in rows. Valid values: \\\"zb\\\" - indicators (statistical metrics), \\\"sj\\\" - time periods (years, quarters, months), \\\"reg\\\" - regions (provinces, cities).\",\n            \"zh\": \"行维度代码，指定行中显示的内容。有效值：\\\"zb\\\" - 指标（统计指标），\\\"sj\\\" - 时间（年、季度、月），\\\"reg\\\" - 地区（省、市）。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"zb\",\n            \"sj\",\n            \"reg\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"colcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Column dimension code specifying what appears in columns. Valid values: \\\"zb\\\" - indicators (statistical metrics), \\\"sj\\\" - time periods (years, quarters, months), \\\"reg\\\" - regions (provinces, cities).\",\n            \"zh\": \"列维度代码，指定列中显示的内容。有效值：\\\"zb\\\" - 指标（统计指标），\\\"sj\\\" - 时间（年、季度、月），\\\"reg\\\" - 地区（省、市）。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"zb\",\n            \"sj\",\n            \"reg\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"wds\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Fixed WHERE dimensions as a JSON array string. Used for additional filtering conditions. Typically use \\\"[]\\\" for empty (no additional filters).\",\n            \"zh\": \"固定WHERE维度，JSON数组字符串。用于附加筛选条件。通常使用\\\"[]\\\"表示空（无附加筛选）。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"dfwds\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Default WHERE dimensions as a JSON array string. Specifies the main filter criteria. For this indicator, use: [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"zb\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"A040D\\\"}] to query by indicator code, or add [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"sj\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"YYYY\\\"}] to filter by specific year.\",\n            \"zh\": \"默认WHERE维度，JSON数组字符串。指定主要筛选条件。对于此指标，使用：[{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"zb\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"A040D\\\"}] 按指标代码查询，或添加 [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"sj\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"YYYY\\\"}] 按特定年份筛选。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"k1\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Timestamp in milliseconds. Used to prevent response caching. Optional - can be omitted or set to current timestamp in milliseconds.\",\n            \"zh\": \"时间戳（毫秒）。用于防止响应缓存。可选 - 可以省略或设置为当前时间戳（毫秒）。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"h\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Optional parameter, typically set to \\\"1\\\". Can be omitted.\",\n            \"zh\": \"可选参数，通常设置为\\\"1\\\"。可以省略。\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"m\": \"QueryData\",\n          \"k1\": \"1766219139509\",\n          \"wds\": \"[]\",\n          \"dfwds\": \"[{\\\"wdcode\\\": \\\"zb\\\", \\\"valuecode\\\": \\\"A040D\\\"}]\",\n          \"dbcode\": \"hgnd\",\n          \"colcode\": \"sj\",\n          \"rowcode\": \"zb\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Data from the National Bureau of Statistics of China (NBSC). This provider offers comprehensive access to official Chinese economic and social statistics data including GDP, population, employment, prices, trade, and more. All data is sourced directly from the official National Bureau of Statistics of China website. The API provides annual, quarterly, and monthly data covering various economic indicators. Data includes national statistics, provincial statistics, major cities data, and Hong Kong, Macao, Taiwan data. No authentication is required to access the public statistics data. This provider includes 107 tools covering different statistical indicators from multiple data sources.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 909.68,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.882\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.financial_statements.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺财报 Financial Statements (Balance/Income/Cash Flow)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query balance sheet, income statement, or cash flow statement data for securities from THS iFinD Financial Statement database using a single entry point.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"statement_type\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Which statement to query: 'balance', 'income', or 'cash_flow'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"year\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Year, e.g., '2024'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"period\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Reporting period: '0331' (Q1), '0630' (H1), '0930' (Q3), '1231' (Annual)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"type\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Report type: '1' (Consolidated), '2' (Parent Company), '3' (Consolidated Adjusted), '4' (Parent Company Adjusted)\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 654.98,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.877\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"nbsc_data.reserve.debit.asset.v2.d24a6f04\",\n      \"name\": \"Debit Reserve Asset\",\n      \"description\": \"Query Debit Reserve Asset statistical data from the National Bureau of Statistics of China. Provides macroeconomic aggregates including GDP, national income, and related indicators. Data available for years 2005 to 2014.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"m\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"API method name. Valid values: \\\"QueryData\\\" - queries statistical data from the database.\",\n            \"zh\": \"API方法名称。有效值：\\\"QueryData\\\" - 从数据库查询统计数据。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"QueryData\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"dbcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Database code specifying the data type and granularity. Valid values: \\\"hgnd\\\" - national annual data, \\\"hgjd\\\" - national quarterly data, \\\"hgyd\\\" - national monthly data, \\\"fsnd\\\" - provincial annual data, \\\"fsjd\\\" - provincial quarterly data, \\\"fsyd\\\" - provincial monthly data.\",\n            \"zh\": \"数据库代码，指定数据类型和粒度。有效值：\\\"hgnd\\\" - 全国年度数据，\\\"hgjd\\\" - 全国季度数据，\\\"hgyd\\\" - 全国月度数据，\\\"fsnd\\\" - 分省年度数据，\\\"fsjd\\\" - 分省季度数据，\\\"fsyd\\\" - 分省月度数据。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"hgnd\",\n            \"hgjd\",\n            \"hgyd\",\n            \"fsnd\",\n            \"fsjd\",\n            \"fsyd\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"rowcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Row dimension code specifying what appears in rows. Valid values: \\\"zb\\\" - indicators (statistical metrics), \\\"sj\\\" - time periods (years, quarters, months), \\\"reg\\\" - regions (provinces, cities).\",\n            \"zh\": \"行维度代码，指定行中显示的内容。有效值：\\\"zb\\\" - 指标（统计指标），\\\"sj\\\" - 时间（年、季度、月），\\\"reg\\\" - 地区（省、市）。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"zb\",\n            \"sj\",\n            \"reg\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"colcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Column dimension code specifying what appears in columns. Valid values: \\\"zb\\\" - indicators (statistical metrics), \\\"sj\\\" - time periods (years, quarters, months), \\\"reg\\\" - regions (provinces, cities).\",\n            \"zh\": \"列维度代码，指定列中显示的内容。有效值：\\\"zb\\\" - 指标（统计指标），\\\"sj\\\" - 时间（年、季度、月），\\\"reg\\\" - 地区（省、市）。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"zb\",\n            \"sj\",\n            \"reg\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"wds\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Fixed WHERE dimensions as a JSON array string. Used for additional filtering conditions. Typically use \\\"[]\\\" for empty (no additional filters).\",\n            \"zh\": \"固定WHERE维度，JSON数组字符串。用于附加筛选条件。通常使用\\\"[]\\\"表示空（无附加筛选）。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"dfwds\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Default WHERE dimensions as a JSON array string. Specifies the main filter criteria. For this indicator, use: [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"zb\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"A020H0303\\\"}] to query by indicator code, or add [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"sj\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"YYYY\\\"}] to filter by specific year.\",\n            \"zh\": \"默认WHERE维度，JSON数组字符串。指定主要筛选条件。对于此指标，使用：[{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"zb\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"A020H0303\\\"}] 按指标代码查询，或添加 [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"sj\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"YYYY\\\"}] 按特定年份筛选。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"k1\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Timestamp in milliseconds. Used to prevent response caching. Optional - can be omitted or set to current timestamp in milliseconds.\",\n            \"zh\": \"时间戳（毫秒）。用于防止响应缓存。可选 - 可以省略或设置为当前时间戳（毫秒）。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"h\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Optional parameter, typically set to \\\"1\\\". Can be omitted.\",\n            \"zh\": \"可选参数，通常设置为\\\"1\\\"。可以省略。\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"m\": \"QueryData\",\n          \"k1\": \"1766219037629\",\n          \"wds\": \"[]\",\n          \"dfwds\": \"[{\\\"wdcode\\\": \\\"zb\\\", \\\"valuecode\\\": \\\"A020H0303\\\"}]\",\n          \"dbcode\": \"hgnd\",\n          \"colcode\": \"sj\",\n          \"rowcode\": \"zb\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Data from the National Bureau of Statistics of China (NBSC). This provider offers comprehensive access to official Chinese economic and social statistics data including GDP, population, employment, prices, trade, and more. All data is sourced directly from the official National Bureau of Statistics of China website. The API provides annual, quarterly, and monthly data covering various economic indicators. Data includes national statistics, provincial statistics, major cities data, and Hong Kong, Macao, Taiwan data. No authentication is required to access the public statistics data. This provider includes 107 tools covering different statistical indicators from multiple data sources.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 830.11,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.56\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.live_prices.retrieve.v1.178541d4\",\n      \"name\": \"Live (Delayed) Stock Prices\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieve live or delayed stock prices and macroeconomic data.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"ticker\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Ticker symbol with exchange suffix (e.g., AAPL.US).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Optional filter parameter.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"ticker\": \"AAPL.US\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1207.16,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.946\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"36fc8a41-1cd7-4078-b722-ad7b609fa94c\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 219.79\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7451,"aggregated":"{\n  \"query\": \"stock price API China\",\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.real_time_quotation.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺实时行情 (THS Real-time Quotation)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query real-time quotation data for securities in the 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database, providing real-time market data for financial products including stocks, funds, bonds, and futures, such as real-time prices, trading volumes, price changes, bid/ask quotes, etc. Supports querying various real-time indicators including latest price, price change, trading volume, turnover ratio, market value, and five-level bid/ask quotes.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"indicators\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Indicator list, multiple indicators separated by commas. Options: 'common' (common indicators), 'all' (all indicators), or custom indicator list. Default is 'all'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"codes\": \"300033.SZ,600030.SH\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1667.64,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.887\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.hk_connect_stats.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 沪深港通交易统计 (HK Stock Connect Trading Stats)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query Shanghai-Shenzhen-Hong Kong Stock Connect trading statistics from 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database. Covers northbound (沪股通, 深股通) and southbound (港股通沪市, 港股通深市) channels. Returns trading volume, buy/sell amounts, net buy amount, transaction counts, and top-10 active stocks concentration ratios. Supports daily, weekly, monthly, and yearly aggregation. Useful for tracking cross-border capital flows between mainland China and Hong Kong markets.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sdate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Start date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"edate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"End date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"zq\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Aggregation period. Valid values: 'day', 'week', 'month', 'year'. Defaults to 'week'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"lx\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Channel type filter. 'ALL'=all channels, '1'=沪股通, '2'=港股通(沪市), '3'=深股通, '4'=港股通(深市). Defaults to 'ALL'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"bz\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Currency for amounts. Defaults to 'CNY'.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 715.71,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.532\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"nbsc_data.(current.price).v2.A0101\",\n      \"name\": \"National Quarterly Data Gdp (current Price)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query National Quarterly Data Gdp (current Price) statistical data from the National Bureau of Statistics of China. Data source: National quarterly data. Provides price indices including consumer prices and producer prices. Data available for periods 2024B to 2025C.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"m\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"API method name. Valid values: \\\"QueryData\\\" - queries statistical data from the database.\",\n            \"zh\": \"API方法名称。有效值：\\\"QueryData\\\" - 从数据库查询统计数据。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"QueryData\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"dbcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Database code specifying the data type and granularity. Valid values: \\\"hgjd\\\" - national quarterly data.\",\n            \"zh\": \"数据库代码，指定数据类型和粒度。有效值：\\\"hgjd\\\" - 全国季度数据。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"hgjd\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"rowcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Row dimension code specifying what appears in rows. Valid values: \\\"zb\\\" - indicators (statistical metrics), \\\"sj\\\" - time periods (years, quarters, months), \\\"reg\\\" - regions (provinces, cities).\",\n            \"zh\": \"行维度代码，指定行中显示的内容。有效值：\\\"zb\\\" - 指标（统计指标），\\\"sj\\\" - 时间（年、季度、月），\\\"reg\\\" - 地区（省、市）。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"zb\",\n            \"sj\",\n            \"reg\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"colcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Column dimension code specifying what appears in columns. Valid values: \\\"zb\\\" - indicators (statistical metrics), \\\"sj\\\" - time periods (years, quarters, months), \\\"reg\\\" - regions (provinces, cities).\",\n            \"zh\": \"列维度代码，指定列中显示的内容。有效值：\\\"zb\\\" - 指标（统计指标），\\\"sj\\\" - 时间（年、季度、月），\\\"reg\\\" - 地区（省、市）。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"zb\",\n            \"sj\",\n            \"reg\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"wds\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Fixed WHERE dimensions as a JSON array string. Used for additional filtering conditions. Typically use \\\"[]\\\" for empty (no additional filters).\",\n            \"zh\": \"固定WHERE维度，JSON数组字符串。用于附加筛选条件。通常使用\\\"[]\\\"表示空（无附加筛选）。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"dfwds\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Default WHERE dimensions as a JSON array string. Specifies the main filter criteria. For this indicator, use: [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"zb\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"A0101\\\"}] to query by indicator code, or add [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"sj\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"YYYY\\\"}] to filter by specific year.\",\n            \"zh\": \"默认WHERE维度，JSON数组字符串。指定主要筛选条件。对于此指标，使用：[{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"zb\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"A0101\\\"}] 按指标代码查询，或添加 [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"sj\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"YYYY\\\"}] 按特定年份筛选。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"k1\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Timestamp in milliseconds. Used to prevent response caching. Optional - can be omitted or set to current timestamp in milliseconds.\",\n            \"zh\": \"时间戳（毫秒）。用于防止响应缓存。可选 - 可以省略或设置为当前时间戳（毫秒）。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"h\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Optional parameter, typically set to \\\"1\\\". Can be omitted.\",\n            \"zh\": \"可选参数，通常设置为\\\"1\\\"。可以省略。\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"m\": \"QueryData\",\n          \"k1\": \"1766394071574\",\n          \"wds\": \"[]\",\n          \"dfwds\": \"[{\\\"wdcode\\\": \\\"zb\\\", \\\"valuecode\\\": \\\"A0101\\\"}]\",\n          \"dbcode\": \"hgjd\",\n          \"colcode\": \"sj\",\n          \"rowcode\": \"zb\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Data from the National Bureau of Statistics of China (NBSC). This provider offers comprehensive access to official Chinese economic and social statistics data including GDP, population, employment, prices, trade, and more. All data is sourced directly from the official National Bureau of Statistics of China website. The API provides annual, quarterly, and monthly data covering various economic indicators. Data includes national statistics, provincial statistics, major cities data, and Hong Kong, Macao, Taiwan data. No authentication is required to access the public statistics data. This provider includes 107 tools covering different statistical indicators from multiple data sources.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 850.39,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.419\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.company_basics.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 公司基础信息 (Company Basics)\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieve the latest (or a specific date) company basics indicators from THS iFinD. Includes company name, industry, comparable/peer companies, concept tags, codes, established date, registration info, main business, and major products.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, comma-separated (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"date\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Date, format: 'YYYYMMDD'. Use this field to query historical values. Defaults to latest.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 780.08,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.914\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.etf_constituents.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD ETF成分股票列表 (ETF Constituent Stock List)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query the constituent stock list of an ETF from 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database. Returns detailed information about each constituent stock including stock code, name, share quantity, cash substitution flag, subscription/redemption premium ratios and fixed substitution amounts. Useful for analyzing ETF composition and tracking ETF holdings.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"thscode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"ETF security code, e.g., '510300.SH', '159001.SZ'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"date\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Query date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'. Defaults to today.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 644.44,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.91\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub_io_api.stock.quote\",\n      \"name\": \"Quote\",\n      \"description\": \"Get real-time quote data for US stocks.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Stock symbol\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 853.46,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.951\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"nbsc_data.self-employed.v2.635e8422\",\n      \"name\": \"Self-employed\",\n      \"description\": \"Query Self-employed statistical data from the National Bureau of Statistics of China. Provides employment statistics including workforce numbers and wage data. Data available for years 2015 to 2024.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"m\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"API method name. Valid values: \\\"QueryData\\\" - queries statistical data from the database.\",\n            \"zh\": \"API方法名称。有效值：\\\"QueryData\\\" - 从数据库查询统计数据。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"QueryData\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"dbcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Database code specifying the data type and granularity. Valid values: \\\"hgnd\\\" - national annual data, \\\"hgjd\\\" - national quarterly data, \\\"hgyd\\\" - national monthly data, \\\"fsnd\\\" - provincial annual data, \\\"fsjd\\\" - provincial quarterly data, \\\"fsyd\\\" - provincial monthly data.\",\n            \"zh\": \"数据库代码，指定数据类型和粒度。有效值：\\\"hgnd\\\" - 全国年度数据，\\\"hgjd\\\" - 全国季度数据，\\\"hgyd\\\" - 全国月度数据，\\\"fsnd\\\" - 分省年度数据，\\\"fsjd\\\" - 分省季度数据，\\\"fsyd\\\" - 分省月度数据。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"hgnd\",\n            \"hgjd\",\n            \"hgyd\",\n            \"fsnd\",\n            \"fsjd\",\n            \"fsyd\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"rowcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Row dimension code specifying what appears in rows. Valid values: \\\"zb\\\" - indicators (statistical metrics), \\\"sj\\\" - time periods (years, quarters, months), \\\"reg\\\" - regions (provinces, cities).\",\n            \"zh\": \"行维度代码，指定行中显示的内容。有效值：\\\"zb\\\" - 指标（统计指标），\\\"sj\\\" - 时间（年、季度、月），\\\"reg\\\" - 地区（省、市）。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"zb\",\n            \"sj\",\n            \"reg\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"colcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Column dimension code specifying what appears in columns. Valid values: \\\"zb\\\" - indicators (statistical metrics), \\\"sj\\\" - time periods (years, quarters, months), \\\"reg\\\" - regions (provinces, cities).\",\n            \"zh\": \"列维度代码，指定列中显示的内容。有效值：\\\"zb\\\" - 指标（统计指标），\\\"sj\\\" - 时间（年、季度、月），\\\"reg\\\" - 地区（省、市）。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"zb\",\n            \"sj\",\n            \"reg\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"wds\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Fixed WHERE dimensions as a JSON array string. Used for additional filtering conditions. Typically use \\\"[]\\\" for empty (no additional filters).\",\n            \"zh\": \"固定WHERE维度，JSON数组字符串。用于附加筛选条件。通常使用\\\"[]\\\"表示空（无附加筛选）。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"dfwds\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Default WHERE dimensions as a JSON array string. Specifies the main filter criteria. For this indicator, use: [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"zb\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"A040D\\\"}] to query by indicator code, or add [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"sj\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"YYYY\\\"}] to filter by specific year.\",\n            \"zh\": \"默认WHERE维度，JSON数组字符串。指定主要筛选条件。对于此指标，使用：[{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"zb\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"A040D\\\"}] 按指标代码查询，或添加 [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"sj\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"YYYY\\\"}] 按特定年份筛选。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"k1\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Timestamp in milliseconds. Used to prevent response caching. Optional - can be omitted or set to current timestamp in milliseconds.\",\n            \"zh\": \"时间戳（毫秒）。用于防止响应缓存。可选 - 可以省略或设置为当前时间戳（毫秒）。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"h\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Optional parameter, typically set to \\\"1\\\". Can be omitted.\",\n            \"zh\": \"可选参数，通常设置为\\\"1\\\"。可以省略。\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"m\": \"QueryData\",\n          \"k1\": \"1766219139509\",\n          \"wds\": \"[]\",\n          \"dfwds\": \"[{\\\"wdcode\\\": \\\"zb\\\", \\\"valuecode\\\": \\\"A040D\\\"}]\",\n          \"dbcode\": \"hgnd\",\n          \"colcode\": \"sj\",\n          \"rowcode\": \"zb\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Data from the National Bureau of Statistics of China (NBSC). This provider offers comprehensive access to official Chinese economic and social statistics data including GDP, population, employment, prices, trade, and more. All data is sourced directly from the official National Bureau of Statistics of China website. The API provides annual, quarterly, and monthly data covering various economic indicators. Data includes national statistics, provincial statistics, major cities data, and Hong Kong, Macao, Taiwan data. No authentication is required to access the public statistics data. This provider includes 107 tools covering different statistical indicators from multiple data sources.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 909.68,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.882\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.financial_statements.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺财报 Financial Statements (Balance/Income/Cash Flow)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query balance sheet, income statement, or cash flow statement data for securities from THS iFinD Financial Statement database using a single entry point.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"statement_type\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Which statement to query: 'balance', 'income', or 'cash_flow'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"year\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Year, e.g., '2024'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"period\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Reporting period: '0331' (Q1), '0630' (H1), '0930' (Q3), '1231' (Annual)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"type\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Report type: '1' (Consolidated), '2' (Parent Company), '3' (Consolidated Adjusted), '4' (Parent Company Adjusted)\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 654.98,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.877\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"nbsc_data.reserve.debit.asset.v2.d24a6f04\",\n      \"name\": \"Debit Reserve Asset\",\n      \"description\": \"Query Debit Reserve Asset statistical data from the National Bureau of Statistics of China. Provides macroeconomic aggregates including GDP, national income, and related indicators. Data available for years 2005 to 2014.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"m\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"API method name. Valid values: \\\"QueryData\\\" - queries statistical data from the database.\",\n            \"zh\": \"API方法名称。有效值：\\\"QueryData\\\" - 从数据库查询统计数据。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"QueryData\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"dbcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Database code specifying the data type and granularity. Valid values: \\\"hgnd\\\" - national annual data, \\\"hgjd\\\" - national quarterly data, \\\"hgyd\\\" - national monthly data, \\\"fsnd\\\" - provincial annual data, \\\"fsjd\\\" - provincial quarterly data, \\\"fsyd\\\" - provincial monthly data.\",\n            \"zh\": \"数据库代码，指定数据类型和粒度。有效值：\\\"hgnd\\\" - 全国年度数据，\\\"hgjd\\\" - 全国季度数据，\\\"hgyd\\\" - 全国月度数据，\\\"fsnd\\\" - 分省年度数据，\\\"fsjd\\\" - 分省季度数据，\\\"fsyd\\\" - 分省月度数据。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"hgnd\",\n            \"hgjd\",\n            \"hgyd\",\n            \"fsnd\",\n            \"fsjd\",\n            \"fsyd\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"rowcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Row dimension code specifying what appears in rows. Valid values: \\\"zb\\\" - indicators (statistical metrics), \\\"sj\\\" - time periods (years, quarters, months), \\\"reg\\\" - regions (provinces, cities).\",\n            \"zh\": \"行维度代码，指定行中显示的内容。有效值：\\\"zb\\\" - 指标（统计指标），\\\"sj\\\" - 时间（年、季度、月），\\\"reg\\\" - 地区（省、市）。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"zb\",\n            \"sj\",\n            \"reg\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"colcode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Column dimension code specifying what appears in columns. Valid values: \\\"zb\\\" - indicators (statistical metrics), \\\"sj\\\" - time periods (years, quarters, months), \\\"reg\\\" - regions (provinces, cities).\",\n            \"zh\": \"列维度代码，指定列中显示的内容。有效值：\\\"zb\\\" - 指标（统计指标），\\\"sj\\\" - 时间（年、季度、月），\\\"reg\\\" - 地区（省、市）。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"zb\",\n            \"sj\",\n            \"reg\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"wds\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Fixed WHERE dimensions as a JSON array string. Used for additional filtering conditions. Typically use \\\"[]\\\" for empty (no additional filters).\",\n            \"zh\": \"固定WHERE维度，JSON数组字符串。用于附加筛选条件。通常使用\\\"[]\\\"表示空（无附加筛选）。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"dfwds\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Default WHERE dimensions as a JSON array string. Specifies the main filter criteria. For this indicator, use: [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"zb\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"A020H0303\\\"}] to query by indicator code, or add [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"sj\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"YYYY\\\"}] to filter by specific year.\",\n            \"zh\": \"默认WHERE维度，JSON数组字符串。指定主要筛选条件。对于此指标，使用：[{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"zb\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"A020H0303\\\"}] 按指标代码查询，或添加 [{\\\"wdcode\\\":\\\"sj\\\",\\\"valuecode\\\":\\\"YYYY\\\"}] 按特定年份筛选。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"k1\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Timestamp in milliseconds. Used to prevent response caching. Optional - can be omitted or set to current timestamp in milliseconds.\",\n            \"zh\": \"时间戳（毫秒）。用于防止响应缓存。可选 - 可以省略或设置为当前时间戳（毫秒）。\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"h\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Optional parameter, typically set to \\\"1\\\". Can be omitted.\",\n            \"zh\": \"可选参数，通常设置为\\\"1\\\"。可以省略。\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"m\": \"QueryData\",\n          \"k1\": \"1766219037629\",\n          \"wds\": \"[]\",\n          \"dfwds\": \"[{\\\"wdcode\\\": \\\"zb\\\", \\\"valuecode\\\": \\\"A020H0303\\\"}]\",\n          \"dbcode\": \"hgnd\",\n          \"colcode\": \"sj\",\n          \"rowcode\": \"zb\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Data from the National Bureau of Statistics of China (NBSC). This provider offers comprehensive access to official Chinese economic and social statistics data including GDP, population, employment, prices, trade, and more. All data is sourced directly from the official National Bureau of Statistics of China website. The API provides annual, quarterly, and monthly data covering various economic indicators. Data includes national statistics, provincial statistics, major cities data, and Hong Kong, Macao, Taiwan data. No authentication is required to access the public statistics data. This provider includes 107 tools covering different statistical indicators from multiple data sources.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 830.11,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.56\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.live_prices.retrieve.v1.178541d4\",\n      \"name\": \"Live (Delayed) Stock Prices\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieve live or delayed stock prices and macroeconomic data.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"ticker\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Ticker symbol with exchange suffix (e.g., AAPL.US).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Optional filter parameter.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"ticker\": \"AAPL.US\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1207.16,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.946\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"36fc8a41-1cd7-4078-b722-ad7b609fa94c\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 219.79\n}","cwd":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772600975464}}
