{"type":"message","id":"fe06cbb3","parentId":"fa88a004","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:10:35.092Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is clearly a bug in the QVeris platform for the THS iFinD tools. The same parameters consistently fail with \"Missing required query parameter: codes\" regardless of how I format them.\n\nLet me try to see if perhaps there's a different API endpoint or tool version that works. Or maybe I should just try using a different data source. Let me try the EODHD tool which also has stock prices but works for international stocks. Maybe it supports Chinese stocks with a different ticker format.","thinkingSignature":"e987b318673641df80cca829f735ba9594acbce1b268cb74d3fba0014ce840ed"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zzdu72rkoo8w_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs search \"Chinese stock ticker format\" --limit 3","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":39251,"output":162,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53397,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772601030208}}
{"type":"message","id":"6ec8c705","parentId":"fe06cbb3","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:10:41.153Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zzdu72rkoo8w_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Chinese stock ticker format\",\n  \"total\": 3,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.code_converter.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺证券代码转换 (THS Security Code Converter)\",\n      \"description\": \"Convert security codes or security names to 同花顺 (THS) standard code format. Supports querying by security code or security name, can specify security type and market, supports exact match or fuzzy match. Returns converted THS codes and related security information.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"seccode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Security code, e.g., '000001'. Either seccode or secname\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"secname\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Security name, e.g., '平安银行'. Either seccode or secname\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"mode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Query mode: 'seccode' (query by code) or 'secname' (query by name)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sectype\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Security type, e.g., '001' (stock), default is empty (query all types)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"market\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Market code, e.g., '212001' (SSE), '212100' (SZSE), default is empty (query all markets)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tradestatus\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Trading status: '0' (normal trading), '1' (suspended), '2' (all), default is '0'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"isexact\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Exact match: '1' (exact match), '0' (fuzzy match), default is '1'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"mode\": \"seccode\",\n          \"seccode\": \"000001\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 582.28,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.98\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.exchange.symbols.list.v1.8b9f3258\",\n      \"name\": \"List tickers for a given exchange\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieve the list of tickers (symbols) available on a specific exchange.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"exchange_code\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Exchange code (e.g., US for USA)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"fmt\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Response format\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"json\",\n            \"csv\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"exchange_code\": \"US\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1805.83,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.573\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financialmodelingprep.search.symbol.retrieve.v1.a740d332\",\n      \"name\": \"Search companies by symbol or name\",\n      \"description\": \"Search for companies using a query string (symbol, name, etc.) with optional filters; Search for ticker symbols, company names, and exchange details for equity securities and ETFs listed on various exchanges.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"query\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Search query (e.g., ticker symbol or company name)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"number\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results to return\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"exchange\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Filter by exchange (e.g., NASDAQ)\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"query\": \"Apple\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"FMP offers a stock market data API covers real-time stock prices, historical prices and market news to stock fundamentals and company information. We provide one of the most accurate financial data available on the market. You can get historical prices, fundamental data, insider transactions, and much more that goes back 30 years in history.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1090,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.934\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"9a562bc1-3e1d-4414-a2f0