{"type":"message","id":"5db903df","parentId":"9e647d34","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:11:08.000Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Same issue - all ths_ifind tools have this problem. This seems to be a systematic bug in the QVeris platform for the THS iFinD provider. Let me try using a different approach to get Chinese stock data - maybe there's another provider that works.\n\nActually, wait - let me try one more approach. Maybe I need to use a stock info website that I can fetch via web_fetch.\n\nActually, I've spent a lot of time on this. Let me try to report back with what I've found and suggest alternatives. The QVeris THS iFinD tools seem to have a systematic bug where they can't receive parameters correctly.\n\nActually, let me try one more thing - using the Tencent Finance or Sina Finance API directly. Or I can try to access a different API that provides Chinese stock data.\n\nLet me search for a different provider:","thinkingSignature":"12a21fa0cd9dafebfb6a48ce8a03624d9842657018d74942bdd6d2dd0c350dba"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pf1hl7b7js81_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs search \"realtime stock price API Asia\" --limit 10","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":40994,"output":236,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55214,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772601059593}}
{"type":"message","id":"52f21572","parentId":"5db903df","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:11:13.752Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pf1hl7b7js81_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"realtime stock price API Asia\",\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.live_prices.retrieve.v1.178541d4\",\n      \"name\": \"Live (Delayed) Stock Prices\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieve live or delayed stock prices and macroeconomic data.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"ticker\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Ticker symbol with exchange suffix (e.g., AAPL.US).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Optional filter parameter.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"ticker\": \"AAPL.US\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1207.16,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.946\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub_io_api.stock.quote\",\n      \"name\": \"Quote\",\n      \"description\": \"Get real-time quote data for US stocks.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Stock symbol\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"