{"type":"message","id":"e928c33f","parentId":"52f21572","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:11:23.090Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The THS iFinD tools consistently don't work due to what appears to be a platform bug. The same \"missing required query parameter\" error occurs regardless of how I format the parameters.\n\nI need to report to the user that there's an issue with the QVeris THS iFinD real-time quotation tool - it appears to have a systematic bug that prevents parameter passing. Let me also try one more time with a simpler tool to see if the EODHD or Finnhub works.","thinkingSignature":"212999bbef550602241bd9828565ec8ba1e3b2befbaafb0e8ce6058570424a27"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5g8o5o5dx8r2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs execute \"eodhd.live_prices.retrieve.v1.178541d4\" --search-id 3429e9d6-78a3-4b16-a23a-3710e0e87a71 --params '{\"ticker\":\"AAPL.US\"}'","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":43613,"output":207,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57804,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772601073753}}
{"type":"message","id":"5db2a25c","parentId":"e928c33f","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:11:29.658Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5g8o5o5dx8r2_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"execution_id\": \"7e5abebc-b6b7-44a1-8d49-10a557749e1c\",\n  \"result\": {\n    \"status_code\": -1,\n    \"data\": null,\n    \"error_type\": \"configuration_error\",\n    \"error_details\": \"缺少必需的路径参数: 'ticker'\"\n  },\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"error_message\": \"缺少必需的路径参数: 'ticker'\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 350.92,\n  \"cost\": 0\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6564,"aggregated":"{\n  \"execution_id\": \"7e5abebc-b6b7-44a1-8d49-10a557749e1c\",\n  \"result\": {\n    \"status_code\": -1,\n    \"data\": null,\n    \"error_type\": \"configuration_error\",\n    \"error_details\": \"缺少必需的路径参数: 'ticker'\"\n  },\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"error_message\": \"缺少必需的路径参数: 'ticker'\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 350.92,\n  \"cost\": 0\n}","cwd":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772601089656}}
{"type":"message","id":"a6b6a656","parentId":"5db2a25c","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:11:42.249Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is interesting - now it's saying \"path parameter\" instead of \"query parameter\". This suggests the tools have different types of parameters. The error says \"缺少必需的路径参数: 'ticker'\" which is \"Missing required path parameter: 'ticker'\".\n\nThis might mean that for some tools, the parameters need to be passed as part of the URL path, not as query parameters or in the body. This is a quirk of how different APIs work.\n\nGiven all these issues, I should report to the user that:\n1. QVeris THS iFinD tools for Chinese stocks appear to have a systematic bug\n2. The parameters consistently fail to be recognized\n3. I've tried multiple approaches but can't get the real-time stock data via QVeris\n\nLet me try one more thing - checking if maybe I can use a different tool or approach. But I think I've exhausted the options here.","thinkingSignature":"c0f0a91320bfb457724fb57e27cd22cf3cd50fd4cdef5bec0c64eebcfb5f88dc"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉，QVeris同花顺实时行情工具存在系统性问题。我尝试了多种方式调用 `ths_ifind.real_time_quotation.v1` 工具，但都遇到相同的错误：\"缺少必需的查询参数: 'codes'\"。\n\n这似乎是QVeris平台在处理同花顺iFinD数据提供商的参数时存在bug - 无论参数格式如何都无法正确传递。\n\n**尝试过的方法：**\n- 使用逗号分隔的股票代码格式（如文档示例：`300033.SZ,600030.SH`）\n- 使用单只股票代码测试\n- 尝试多个相关的iFinD工具（company_basics, code_converter等）\n- 尝试其他股票API提供商（EODHD、Finnhub）\n\n所有带 `codes` 参数的同花顺工具都返回相同的参数缺失错误。\n\n**替代方案建议：**\n1. 稍后重试 - 可能是QVeris平台的临时问题\n2. 手动查询股价\n3. 使用其他数据源\n\n如需继续尝试，请告诉我。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":43955,"output":401,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58340,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772601089658}}
